Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Small earthquake in 'Frisco
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040byhn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Aug 1979
Small San Francisco earthquake sparks big headlines. Small announcement of Irish peace talks sparks Whitehall annoyance. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less